p://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Aaron D. Campbell\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1972:\"<p>We just released version 0.3.4 of the <a href=\"http://xavisys.com/wordpress-plugins/efficient-related-posts/\">Efficient Related Posts plugin for WordPress</a>.  It uses the new Xavisys Plugin Framwork (I&#8217;ll post more info on that soon), which gives it a nice new options page, links to the support forums, etc.  We also did a lot of the work toward internationalizing it, and hopefully it will be fully translatable int he next version (coming soon).</p>\n<p>If you want to request a feature, or need support, go to the <a href=\"http://xavisys.com/support/forum/efficient-related-posts/\">Efficient Related Posts Support Forum</a>.  More information is available on the <a href=\"http://xavisys.com/wordpress-plugins/efficient-related-posts/\">Efficient Related Posts</a> page.<br />\n<h3 class=\'related_post_title\'>Related Posts:</h3>\n<ul class=\'related_post\'>\n<li><a href=\'http://xavisys.com/problem-related-post-plugins/\' title=\'The Problem with Related Post Plugins\'>The Problem with Related Post Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://xavisys.com/xavisys-wordpress-plugin-framework/\' title=\'The Xavisys WordPress Plugin Framework\'>The Xavisys WordPress Plugin Framework</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://xavisys.com/10-great-wordpress-plugins/\' title=\'10 Great WordPress Plugins\'>10 Great WordPress Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://xavisys.com/wordpress-plugins/manual-related-links/\' title=\'Manual Related Links\'>Manual Related Links</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://xavisys.com/wordpress-plugins/efficient-related-posts/\' title=\'Efficient Related Posts\'>Efficient Related Posts</a></li>\n</ul>\n<span class=\"sfforumlink\"><a href=\"http://xavisys.com/support/forum/efficient-related-posts/efficient-related-posts-0-3-4-released/\"><img src=\"http://xavisys.com/wp-content/plugins/simple-forum/styles/icons/default/bloglink.png\" alt=\"\" /> Join the forum discussion on this post</a></span><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Xavisys/~4/HSN_A-a9Zkk\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"http://xavisys.com/efficient-related-posts-0-3-4-released/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://xavisys.com/efficient-related-posts-0-3-4-released/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";s:4:\"href\";s:35:\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/Xavisys\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\