	(5173,0,'_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e','<h4>Most Popular</h4>\n<h5><a href=\'http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wordpress-importer/\'>WordPress Importer</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=wordpress-importer&amp;_wpnonce=c15c3a9eba&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'WordPress Importer\'>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>Import posts, pages, comments, custom fields, categories, tags and more from a WordPress export file.</p>\n<h4>Newest Plugins</h4>\n<h5><a href=\'http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/glossy/\'>Tippy</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=glossy&amp;_wpnonce=4196ea84c1&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'Tippy\'>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>Makes it easy to create site-wide glossary or dictionary entries which pop up using the Tippy plugin</p>\n<h4>Recently Updated</h4>\n<h5><a href=\'http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/shortcode-redirect/\'>Shortcode Redirect</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=shortcode-redirect&amp;_wpnonce=92e33b5a25&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'Shortcode Redirect\'>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>A super easy way to automatically redirect a user to another page when viewing a post/page on your site.</p>\n','no'),
