	(37,1,'2010-09-29 01:03:00','2010-09-29 01:03:00','My Name is Ramon Roche, I\'m a web developer working on the South California area\r\n\r\nContact:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile: 858 699 7759</li>\r\n	<li>Email: mrpollo@gmail.com</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nif you are looking to hire me, my resume can be downloaded by click on <a title=\"My Resume\" href=\"/content/ramonroche-resume.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">This Link</a>','About','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-3','','','2010-09-29 01:03:00','2010-09-29 01:03:00','',2,'http://ramonroche/?p=37',0,'revision','',0),
