	(47,1,'2010-12-27 17:02:16','2010-12-27 17:02:16','Found a great command that shows the progress of a command its called Pipe Viewer and you can find it <a href=\"http://www.ivarch.com/programs/pv.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Here are some examples on usage:</strong>\r\n\r\nfound on this great article:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.catonmat.net/blog/unix-utilities-pipe-viewer/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.catonmat.net/blog/unix-utilities-pipe-viewer/</a>\r\n\r\n<script src=\"https://gist.github.com/943612.js\"> </script>','Pipe Viewer','Found a great command that shows the progress of a command its called Pipe Viewer and you can find it http://www.ivarch.com/programs/pv.shtml.\r\n\r\nHere are some examples on usage:\r\n\r\nfound on this great article:\r\n\r\nhttp://www.catonmat.net/blog/unix-utilities-pipe-viewer/\r\n','publish','open','open','','pipe-viewer','','','2011-06-23 17:45:35','2011-06-23 17:45:35','',0,'http://ramonroche/?p=47',0,'post','',0),
