	(89,1,'2011-01-05 22:25:52','2011-01-05 22:25:52','i know every year we try to do something cool and new, but this year ill try to keep it simple,\r\n\r\nlisten to music with my last.fm app turned on so i get statistics by the end of next year, and on my holidays for next year ill make a set of visualisations, ill gather data depending on my mood, to try and print a picture of what happened and who i was I during this coming year.\r\n\r\nLets just hope the mayans where wrong and that the world isn\'t ending','New Years resolution','','inherit','open','open','','49-revision-2','','','2011-01-05 22:25:52','2011-01-05 22:25:52','',49,'http://ramonroche/2011/01/49-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),
